    Bob
    Ana
*/
```

## do/while Loop
The do/while loop statement has one expressions:
```js
Condition - defines the loop stop condition
do {
    // code block to be executed
} while (condition)
```
Example of do/while loop:
```js
var array = [
    {id: 0, name: 'John', age: 20},
